Working principle of an LSC: (1) The solar radiation reaches the material. (2) The luminescent dye in the material absorbs the incoming radiation. The dye re-emits a down-shifted radiation in every direction. (3) The emitted radiation is guided towards the edge of the material to be collected with a photovoltaic cell
